       DETAIL
*EXP(1
* 709 FORTRAN LIBRARY / EXPONENTIAL ROUTINE - FXPT BASE-FXPT EXP / 9XP1.
* IBM / APPLIED PROGRAMMING / JANUARY 1960.     
*      AUGUST 27,1962   
*     
       REM
       LBL     EXP1
       ENTRY   EXP(1    
       REM     . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .
       REM
 EXP(1 TZE     1,4           EXIT FOR ZERO BASE 
       ARS     18 
       STO     POWER         SAVE NON-ZERO BASE 
       LLS     17            OBTAIN EXPONENT    
       STA     EXP           SAVE EXPONENT
       NZT     EXP           TEST FOR ZERO EXPONENT   
       TRA     OUT           EXIT FOR ZERO EXPONENT   
       CLA     FIXONE   
       SBM     POWER    
       TZE     N  
       TQP     N  
       TRA     EXIT     
 N     CLA     FIXONE   
       STO     FACTOR   
 CLA1  CLA     EXP           IS POWER     
       LBT                   A FACTOR     
       TRA     CLA2          NO     
       LDQ     POWER         YES    
       MPY     FACTOR   
       STQ     FACTOR   
 CLA2  CLA     EXP
       ARS     1  
       STO     EXP
       TZE     EXIT     
       LDQ     POWER         COMPUTE
       MPY     POWER         NEXT   
       STQ     POWER         POWER  
       TRA     CLA1     
 EXIT  LLS     53 
       TRA     1,4
 OUT   CLA     ONE
       TRA     1,4
       REM     . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .
FIXONE DEC     1  
 ONE   PZE     0,0,1    
 EXP   PZE     0  
       REM     WORKING STORAGE
       COMMON  -206     
 POWER COMMON  1  
FACTOR COMMON  1  
       REM     . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .
       END  
